---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import SEOHead from '../../components/SEOHead.astro';
import Navbar from '../../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import FAQSchema from '../../components/FAQSchema.astro';
---

<BaseLayout>
  <SEOHead slot="head" title="Tattoo Studio Referral Program — Automated Referral Tracking" description="InkFlow's referral program automation tracks which clients send you business and rewards your best advocates automatically. 40% higher conversion from referred leads. Start free." />
  <FAQSchema questions={[
    { question: "How does automated referral tracking work?", answer: "Every new client is tagged with their referral source. Track conversion rates by referrer. Reward advocates automatically based on referral volume." },
    { question: "Can I set up automatic rewards?", answer: "Yes. Set reward rules — 5 referrals = $50 credit, 10 referrals = free touch-up. InkFlow tracks and notifies both parties automatically." },
    { question: "Do referred clients convert at higher rates?", answer: "Yes. Referred clients book at 40% higher rates than organic leads. They arrive with trust already established." },
  ]} />
  <Navbar />

  <section class="pt-24 pb-16 sm:pt-32">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-accent-400 mb-3">TATTOO REFERRAL PROGRAM</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-white sm:text-5xl">Referral Program for Tattoo Studios: Automated Tracking &amp; Rewards</h1>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-gray-400">InkFlow's referral program tracks which clients send you business and rewards your best advocates automatically. Referred clients book at 40% higher rates. Word of mouth, automated.</p>
      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
        <a href="https://app.ink-flows.com/register" class="inline-block rounded-lg bg-accent-500 px-8 py-3.5 text-base font-semibold text-ink-950 hover:bg-accent-400 transition-all">Try InkFlow Free →</a>
        <a href="/features/tattoo-crm-software" class="inline-block rounded-lg border border-ink-700 px-8 py-3.5 text-base font-semibold text-white hover:bg-ink-800 transition-all">See CRM Features</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="border-t border-ink-800/50 py-16 bg-ink-900/20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white text-center">Why Most Studios Leave Referral Revenue on the Table</h2>
      <div class="mt-8 space-y-4">
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-ink-800 bg-ink-900/30 p-5"><h3 class="text-white font-semibold text-sm">Referral tracking is guesswork — "how did you hear about us?" forms are unreliable.</h3><p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-400">Clients forget or give vague answers. InkFlow tracks referral sources automatically through booking links and client-shared links.</p></div>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-ink-800 bg-ink-900/30 p-5"><h3 class="text-white font-semibold text-sm">Without automated rewards, referrals happen by accident.</h3><p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-400">Clients who love your work will refer friends — but without a system to track and reward them, referrals are inconsistent. InkFlow automates the entire process.</p></div>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-ink-800 bg-ink-900/30 p-5"><h3 class="text-white font-semibold text-sm">You don't know which clients are your best advocates.</h3><p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-400">Some clients refer constantly. Others never do. InkFlow shows you who your top referrers are so you can nurture those relationships.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="border-t border-ink-800/50 py-16">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white text-center">Referral Program Features</h2>
      <div class="mt-12 space-y-16">
      <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 items-center">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">Full Referral Chain Tracking from Source to Booking</h3>
          <p class="mt-4 text-gray-400">Every new client is tagged with their referral source. Track conversion rates by referrer and see who sends the most business.</p>
          <h4 class="mt-4 text-lg font-semibold text-white">Multi-Touch Attribution</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Track the full referral chain — who shared, who clicked, who booked. Understand which advocates drive the most revenue.</p>
          <h5 class="mt-3 text-base font-medium text-white">40% Higher Conversion from Referral Leads</h5>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Referred clients arrive with trust already established. Shorter sales cycle, higher average spend, better retention.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl bg-ink-900/50 border border-ink-800 p-8 text-center">
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">[Screenshot: Referral tracking]</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 items-center">
        <div class="order-2 md:order-1 rounded-xl bg-ink-900/50 border border-ink-800 p-8 text-center">
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">[Screenshot: Reward settings]</p>
        </div>
        <div class="order-1 md:order-2">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">Automatic Rewards Based on Referral Volume</h3>
          <p class="mt-4 text-gray-400">Set reward rules — 5 referrals = $50 studio credit, 10 = free touch-up. InkFlow tracks and notifies both parties automatically.</p>
          <h4 class="mt-4 text-lg font-semibold text-white">Tiered Reward System</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Create unlimited reward tiers. Gold, Silver, Bronze — or custom names that match your studio's brand. Each tier unlocks automatically.</p>
          <h5 class="mt-3 text-base font-medium text-white">Automated Notification + Fulfillment</h5>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">When a client unlocks a reward, both parties receive automatic notification. Credits are applied to the client's account instantly.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- BUYER GUIDE -->
  <section class="border-t border-ink-800/50 py-16 bg-ink-900/20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white text-center">Is a Referral Program Right for Your Studio?</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-center text-gray-400">Referral programs work best when you have a strong base of happy clients.</p>
      <div class="mt-8 space-y-4">
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-ink-800 bg-ink-900/30 p-5"><h3 class="text-white font-semibold text-sm">New studio building a client base</h3><p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-1">Start tracking referrals manually or use InkFlow's free referral tracking. Identify your first advocates and reward them early.</p></div>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-ink-800 bg-ink-900/30 p-5"><h3 class="text-white font-semibold text-sm">Established studio with 100+ active clients</h3><p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-1">Automated referral tracking and rewards unlock growth from your existing client base. InkFlow identifies advocates you didn't know you had.</p></div>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-ink-800 bg-ink-900/30 p-5"><h3 class="text-white font-semibold text-sm">Multi-location studio chain</h3><p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-1">Track referrals per location. Compare which studios generate the most word-of-mouth. Share best practices across locations.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="border-t border-ink-800/50 py-16 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">Turn Clients Into Your Marketing Team</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 text-gray-400">Free plan includes referral tracking. Upgrade for automated rewards.</p>
    <a href="https://app.ink-flows.com/register" class="mt-6 inline-block rounded-lg bg-accent-500 px-8 py-3.5 text-base font-semibold text-ink-950 hover:bg-accent-400 transition-all">Try InkFlow Free →</a>
    <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-600">Also available in <a href="/features/tattoo-crm-software" class="text-accent-400 hover:underline">CRM Features</a></p>
  </section>
  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
